400000173307/M21-1-Part-XIV-Chapter-7-Data-Matching-Programs-That-Identify-Incarcerated-Beneficiaries-and-Dependents\">M21-1, Part XIV, 7</a></span></span></div></li><li><div><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">fugitive felon status, see <a articleid=\"554400000173306\" articlename=\"M21-1, Part XIV, Chapter 8 - Fugitive Felon Match\" articleviewcontext=\"article_view_related_article\" class=\"eGainArticleLink\" eg-link-click=\"\" href=\"/system/templates/selfservice/va_ssnew/help/customer/locale/en-US/portal/554400000001018/content/554400000173306/M21-1-Part-XIV-Chapter-8-Fugitive-Felon-Match\">M21-1, Part XIV, 8</a></span></span></div></li><li><div><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">military pay adjustments, see <a articleid=\"554400000179487\" articlename=\"M21-1, Part VI, Subpart ii, Chapter 4, Section A - Elections and Waivers in Military Retired Pay (MRP) Cases\" articleviewcontext=\"article_view_related_article\" class=\"eGainArticleLink\" eg-link-click=\"\" href=\"/system/templates/selfservice/va_ssnew/help/customer/locale/en-US/portal/554400000001018/content/554400000179487/M21-1-Part-VI-Subpart-ii-Chapter-4-Section-A-Elections-and-Waivers-in-Military-Retired-Pay-MRP-Cases\">M21-1, Part VI, Subpart ii, 4.A</a>-<a articleid=\"554400000179491\" articlename=\"M21-1, Part VI, Subpart ii, Chapter 4, Section E - Processing Audit Error Worksheets (AEWs)\" articleviewcontext=\"article_view_related_article\" class=\"eGainArticleLink\" eg-link-click=\"\" href=\"/system/templates/selfservice/va_ssnew/help/customer/locale/en-US/portal/554400000001018/content/554400000179491/M21-1-Part-VI-Subpart-ii-Chapter-4-Section-E-Processing-Audit-Error-Worksheets-AEWs\">E</a>, and</span></span></div></li><li><div><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">returned payments, see <a articleid=\"554400000179502\" articlename=\"M21-1, Part VI, Subpart iii, Chapter 4 - Disappearance and Reappearance of a Veteran\" articleviewcontext=\"article_view_related_article\" class=\"eGainArticleLink\" eg-link-click=\"\" href=\"/system/templates/selfservice/va_ssnew/help/customer/locale/en-US/portal/554400000001018/content/554400000179502/M21-1-Part-VI-Subpart-iii-Chapter-4-Disappearance-and-Reappearance-of-a-Veteran\">M21-1, Part VI, Subpart iii, 4</a>.</span></span></div></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table><div class=\"ng-scope\" style=\"margin-left: 85pt\"><hr/></div><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"ng-scope\" style=\"border-spacing: 0px; border-collapse: revert;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"width: 115px; vertical-align: top; padding: 0px;\"><h3><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">I.ii.1.D.1.d<a id=\"1d\" name=\"1d\">.</a>  Types of Unique Eligibility Decisions </span></span></h3></td><td style=\"height: 8px; width: 15px; padding: 0px;\"></td><td style=\"width: 516px; padding: 0px;\"><div><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">BEST sites also process unique eligibility decisions like initial character of discharge determinations, attorney fee eligibility related to non-rating issues, administrative decisions on healthcare and home loan eligibility, as well as debt validation requests referred by the Debt Management Center.</span></span></div><div></div><div><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><b><i>References</i></b>:  For more information on</span></span></div><ul><li><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">character-of-discharge (COD) determinations, see <a articleid=\"554400000177986\" articlename=\"M21-1, Part X, Subpart iv, Chapter 1, Section A  - Character of Discharge (COD) and Bars to Benefits\" articleviewcontext=\"article_view_related_article\" class=\"eGainArticleLink\" eg-link-click=\"\" href=\"/system/templates/selfservice/va_ssnew/help/customer/locale/en-US/portal/554400000001018/content/554400000177986/M21-1-Part-X-Subpart-iv-Chapter-1-Section-A-Character-of-Discharge-COD-and-Bars-to-Benefits\">M21-1, Part X, Subpart iv, 1.A</a></span></span></li><li><div><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">home loan eligibility and COD determinations, see <a articleid=\"554400000173831\" articlename=\"M21-1, Part XIII, Subpart i, Chapter 7, Section A - Department of Veterans Affairs (VA) Home Loan Program\" articleviewcontext=\"article_view_related_article\" class=\"eGainArticleLink\" eg-link-click=\"\" href=\"/system/templates/selfservice/va_ssnew/help/customer/locale/en-US/portal/554400000001018/content/554400000173831/M21-1-Part-XIII-Subpart-i-Chapter-7-Section-A-Department-of-Veterans-Affairs-VA-Home-Loan-Program\">M21-1, Part XIII, Subpart i, 7.A.2.b</a></span></span></div></li><li><div><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">debt validation requests, see <a articleid=\"554400000179498\" articlename=\"M21-1, Part VI, Subpart iii, Chapter 2, Section C - Debt Disputes and Collection\" articleviewcontext=\"article_view_related_article\" class=\"eGainArticleLink\" eg-link-click=\"\" href=\"/system/templates/selfservice/va_ssnew/help/customer/locale/en-US/portal/554400000001018/content/554400000179498/M21-1-Part-VI-Subpart-iii-Chapter-2-Section-C-Debt-Disputes-and-Collection\">M21-1, Part VI, Subpart iii, 2.C.2.a</a></span></span></div></li><li><div><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">eligibility for medical services, see <a articleid=\"554400000173640\" articlename=\"M21-1, Part XIII, Subpart i, Chapter 3, Section A - General Information on Eligibility for Medical Services\" articleviewcontext=\"article_view_related_article\" class=\"eGainArticleLink\" eg-link-click=\"\" href=\"/system/templates/selfservice/va_ssnew/help/customer/locale/en-US/portal/554400000001018/content/554400000173640/M21-1-Part-XIII-Subpart-i-Chapter-3-Section-A-General-Information-on-Eligibility-for-Medical-Services\">M21-1, Part XIII, Subpart i, 3.A</a>, and</span></span></div></li><li><div><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">attorney fees, see <a articleid=\"554400000205495\" articlename=\"M21-5, Chapter 8, Section A - Introduction to Fees\" articleviewcontext=\"article_view_related_article\" class=\"eGainArticleLink\" eg-link-click=\"\" href=\"/system/templates/selfservice/va_ssnew/help/customer/locale/en-US/portal/554400000001018/content/554400000205495/M21-5-Chapter-8-Section-A-Introduction-to-Fees\">M21-5, Chapter 8.A</a>. </span></span></div></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table><div class=\"ng-scope\" style=\"margin-left: 85pt\"><hr/></div><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"ng-scope\" style=\"border-spacing: 0px; border-collapse: revert;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"width: 115px; vertical-align: top; padding: 0px;\"><h3><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">I.ii.1.D.1.e<a id=\"1e\" name=\"1e\">.</a>  Additional Responsibilities of BEST Sites</span></span></h3></td><td style=\"height: 8px; width: 15px; padding: 0px;\"></td><td style=\"width: 516px; padding: 0px;\"><div><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">In addition to general workload oversight, BEST sites are responsible for responding to inquiries submitted through the <a href=\"https://ask.va.gov/\" target=\"_blank\">Ask VA</a> platform and to the Secretary of VA (SecVA) mailbox.</span></span></div></td></tr></tbody></table><div class=\"ng-scope\" style=\"margin-left: 85pt\"><hr/></div><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"ng-scope\" style=\"border-spacing: 0px; border-collapse: revert;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"width: 115px; vertical-align: top; padding: 0px;\"><h3><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">I.ii.1.D.1.f<a id=\"1f\" name=\"1f\">.</a>  Structure of BEST Sites </span></span> </h3></td><td style=\"height: 8px; width: 15px; padding: 0px;\"></td><td style=\"width: 516px; padding: 0px;\"><div><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">BEST sites maintain a similar structure to regional offices in terms of supervisor oversight, claims processors, and quality reviewers.   However, BEST sites do not contain a rating activity.  Workload that involves rating decisions will be the responsibility of Veterans Service Centers, Pension Management Centers, Decision Review Operation Centers, and Disability Rating Activity Sites, as applicable.</span></span></div><div></div><div><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Assignment of workload that also involves special missions and circumstances, or hearing requests, is determined by OFO and further detailed in the <a href=\"https://dvagov.sharepoint.com/sites/VACOOFOGeneral/SitePages/Home.aspx\" target=\"_blank\"><i>Non-Rating Resource Job Aid</i></a>.</span></span></div></td></tr></tbody></table><div class=\"ng-scope\" style=\"margin-left: 85pt\"><hr/></div><div class=\"ng-scope\"></div><p class=\"ng-scope\" style=\"text-align: right\"><span style=\"font-size:11px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><a articleid=\"554400000181484\" articlename=\"M21-1, Part I, Subpart ii, Chapter 1, Section C - Pension Management Center (PMC) Procedures\" articleviewcontext=\"article_view_related_article\" class=\"eGainArticleLink\" eg-link-click=\"\" href=\"/system/templates/selfservice/va_ssnew/help/customer/locale/en-US/portal/554400000001018/content/554400000181484/M21-1-Part-I-Subpart-ii-Chapter-1-Section-C-Pension-Management-Center-PMC-Procedures\"> &lt;-- Previous Section</a>  <a articleid=\"554400000181485\" articlename=\"M21-1, Part I, Subpart ii, Chapter 2 - Department of Veterans Affairs (VA) Benefit Programs\" articleviewcontext=\"article_view_related_article\" class=\"eGainArticleLink\" eg-link-click=\"\" href=\"/system/templates/selfservice/va_ssnew/help/customer/locale/en-US/portal/554400000001018/content/554400000181485/M21-1-Part-I-Subpart-ii-Chapter-2-Department-of-Veterans-Affairs-VA-Benefit-Programs\">Next Section --&gt;</a></span></span></p><p class=\"ng-scope\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span style=\"font-family: arial , helvetica , sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 11px\"><a href=\"#top\" target=\"_self\">To Top</a></span></span></p><p class=\"ng-scope\"></p></div>\n</div>",
